// `double` is intentionally not declared as a FnDeclaration in this program.
// It exercises the "extern / imported user function" path in the analyzer:
// the analyzer treats it as O(1) (StreamFunctionKind::UserDefined with no fn_map entry),
// but the absence of a FnDeclaration means assumes_o1_user_fns remains false.
range(0, 10).map(double).return
